
MeshBerry - lib directory
=========================

This directory is intended for project-specific (private) libraries.
PlatformIO will compile them into a static library and link into the executable.

The source code of each library should be placed in a separate directory:

|--lib
|  |
|  |--CustomLibrary
|  |  |--src
|  |  |  |- CustomLibrary.cpp
|  |  |  |- CustomLibrary.h
|  |  |--library.json (optional)
|  |
|  |--README (this file)

More information:
https://docs.platformio.org/page/librarymanager/ldf.html

External libraries are managed via platformio.ini lib_deps:
- TFT_eSPI (display driver)
- RadioLib (LoRa SX1262)
- TinyGPSPlus (GPS NMEA parsing)
- ArduinoJson (configuration files)

Place any custom MeshBerry libraries here (e.g., mesh protocol wrappers).
